1. Pass `proxy` from the callback into `applyDiff()`.
2. Replace all `down.post(tap: .cgSessionEventTap)` / `up.post(tap: .cgSessionEventTap)` calls with `CGEventTapPostEvent(proxy, down)` / `CGEventTapPostEvent(proxy, up)`.
